body_html:
I got the same issue
Just upgarde build grade as the same version as your android studio version
for mine is:
dependencies {
classpath 'com.android.tools.build:gradle:3.1.4' // android studio 3.1.4
classpath 'org.apache.httpcomponents:httpclient:4.5.4'
}

then you can run and see TF sample apk installed: TF Classify, TF Detect, TF Speech, TF Stylize
